    dc:description "FIGURES 25 – 30. Specimens of Camaegeria Strand, 1914, Episannina perlucida (Le Cerf, 1911) and Tipulamima haugi (Le Cerf, 1917). Scale bar: 10 mm. 25 – 26. C. lychnitis n. sp., 3 holotype, upperside (25), underside (26). 27. Episannina perlucida (Le Cerf, 1911), 3 lectotype. 28 – 29. C. viettei n. sp., 3 holotype, upperside (28), underside (29). 30. Tipulamima haugi (Le Cerf, 1917), 3 syntype." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/212260/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.212265>
    dc:description "FIGURES 36 – 37. Male genitalia of Camaegeria Strand, 1914. 36. Camaegeria lychnitis n. sp. 37. Camaegeria viettei n. sp." ;
